    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the centrifugal blood pump design meets the hemolysis acceptance criterion (RH < 1) across the worst-case operating envelope. The assessment is consistent with all project requirements documented in PRJ-REQ-2024-001.",
